    "en": "thermal power loss caused by the over- current in a short-circuit or in a situation equivalent to a short-circuit measured at  given duration and at rated ambient temperature"
  },
  "synonyms": [],
  "note": "Examples for situations equivalent to a short circuit:\r\n- transformer with the second winding short-circuited;\r\n- motor with rotor blocked caused by operational or fault events.",
